{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"20773-my-family","title":"Mi Familia","description":"Tengo una gran familia ¿Te gustaría conocerla?","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Roberto Palma"],"illustrators":["Rajeev Verma 'Banjara'"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/20773-my-family"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/534571/size3/9c37e0f0dfbdd4fbb5a4aada16598c88.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/534571/size6/9c37e0f0dfbdd4fbb5a4aada16598c88.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42295/size6/7bef0e9eed187cb6e47be5fe02a76b5d.jpg","text":"Yo soy Tuktuk.\nTengo una gran familia.\nConozcámosla...","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42296/size6/08ae36abf079b6e0a62f55fccf9d9a95.jpg","text":"Ella es mi madre y él es mi padre.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42297/size6/43e6ca9b2c60c1bdab4911ee76c8e601.jpg","text":"´Él es mi hermano, Neetu, y ella es mi hermana, Meetu. Miren...","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42298/size6/d1694f6c1f0b81b27b08ccdf97a9701e.jpg","text":"Y ahora, mis abuelos paternos y maternos también están aquí.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42299/size6/8f71aa2df40ef8a6512567991ec7f0c7.jpg","text":"Mi mamá tiene tres hermanas.\nYo las llamo Tías. Y miren...","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42300/size6/bcb62885ca36d202c631e0f4b75446fb.jpg","text":"Mi papá tiene cuatro hermanos.\nDos mayores y dos menores. Además...","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42301/size6/8a7a9a52ad4535e8986dab29b2e71a41.jpg","text":"están sus esposas, dos tías mayores y dos tías menores.\nMiren, mire, miren...","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42302/size6/b10c12c3059e0f309b5bb3ca76523dfb.jpg","text":"En mi familia también hay cinco niños pequeños.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42303/size6/3ee7e1a1c919ac7657c40b6279d6c0b2.jpg","text":"Y nos divertimos mucho todos juntos.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42304/size6/57d97b94e97558435ae940550e539758.jpg","text":"¡Miren! ¡Qué grande es mi familia!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42305/size6/4665bb9675035e515b8b8260ad039d4c.jpg","text":"¡Esperen, esperen! Olvidé a Buzo,\nque mueve su cola y ladra todo el día...\n¡Guau, guau, guau!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":111}}